trans-unit.source: Describes a reference to a collection of XML Web services.
trans-unit.target: Beskriver en referanse til en samling av XML-webtjenesten.

trans-unit.source: A WebReference object is used to pass information about a set of Web services to the static <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> class.
trans-unit.target: En WebReference-objektet til å sende informasjon om et sett med nettjenester til statisk <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences%2A>metode for <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>klasse.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference"></xref> class with the given description document collection and proxy code namespace.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference"> </xref> klasse angitt beskrivelse dokumentet samlingen og proxy kode navneområdet.

trans-unit.source: The `documents` collection should contain only <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> and <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> objects; the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences%2A> method is unable to interpret <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument> objects.
trans-unit.target: Den `documents` samlingen må inneholde bare <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>og <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>objekter; den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences%2A>metoden er ikke tolke <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument>objekter.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref> that specifies a collection of description documents.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"> </xref> som angir en samling med beskrivelse dokumenter.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespace"></xref> that specifies a namespace for code compilation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespace"> </xref> som angir et navneområde for koden kompilering.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the base URL of the Web reference.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder den primære URL-adressen for Web-referanse.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the URL key of the web reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter URL-nøkkelen for webreferanse.

trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder nøkkelen URL-adressen for Web-referanse.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of description documents associated with the Web reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av beskrivelse dokumenter som er knyttet til Web-referansen.

trans-unit.source: The description document collection associated with a Web reference should contain only <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> and <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> objects; the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences%2A> method is unable to interpret <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument> objects.
trans-unit.target: Beskrivelse dokumentsamlingen knyttet til en webreferanse må inneholde bare <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>og <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>objekter; den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences%2A>metoden er ikke tolke <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument>objekter.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref> used to initialize the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"> </xref> brukes til å starte den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the protocol associated with the Web reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir protokollen som er knyttet til Web-referansen.

trans-unit.source: Allowed protocol strings include "Soap" (indicating SOAP 1.0) and "Soap12" (indicating SOAP 1.2).
trans-unit.target: Tillatt protokollen strengene inneholde "Soap" (som viser SOAP 1.0) og "Soap12" (som viser SOAP 1.2).

trans-unit.source: The value of this property determines the protocol used by proxy clients when contacting any XML Web service in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference.Documents%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen bestemmer protokollen som brukes av proxy-klienter ved å kontakte en XML-webtjenesten i den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference.Documents%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference.Documents%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information on SOAP, see the World Wide Web Consortium Web site, at www.w3.org.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om SOAP, kan du se World Wide Web Consortium webområdet, på www.w3.org.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the name of the protocol associated with the Web reference.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder navnet på protokollen som er knyttet til Web-referansen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the code namespace associated with the Web reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter navneområdet kode som er knyttet til Web-referansen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespace"></xref> in which proxy code will be generated when the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences*> method is called.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespace"> </xref> hvilken proxy-koden blir generert når den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences*>-metoden.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.GenerateWebReferences*>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of warnings generated when validating the description documents.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling med advarsler som genereres når du validerer beskrivelse-dokumenter.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection"></xref> of validation warning text.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection"> </xref> tekstens validering advarsel.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of warnings generated when importing Web Services Description Language (WSDL) service description documents.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling med advarsler genereres under import av Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL) service beskrivelse dokumenter.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportWarnings"></xref> collection of warnings generated when importing WSDL service description documents.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportWarnings"> </xref> samling advarsler genereres under import av WSDL tjenesten beskrivelse dokumenter.
